<div class="author-info u-clearfix">
	<% if (theme.avatar) { %>
	<img class="avatar" src="<%= config.root %>img/avatar.png" alt="<%= config.author %>">
	<% } %>
	<div class="author-content">
		<div class="author-description">
			<p>本文作者：<%= config.author %></p>
			<p><%= theme.signature %></p>
			<p>原文链接：
				<a href="<%= post.permalink %>"><%= post.permalink %></a>
			</p>
			<b>本站文章如无特殊声明均为原创，创作不易，转载请注明来源，谢谢！</b>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>